description.en:
The InuYasha ecosystem will exist as a decentralised vetting and donation program for promising new tokens. New teams will submit their soon to launch Protocol, Blockchain Game, Meme Token, or any project, charity, org that wishes to apply for a donation from our community.

Application by potential project – Decentralised vetting by InuYasha holders
Donation recipient gives InuYasha holders pre sale access
Winner receives a boost in donation and marketing by the InuYasha community
InuYasha holders will get the earliest access to community vetted and 100% safe projects.
